item.title: CVE-2020-2323|2024-08-04T07:09:54.327Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20chaos%20monkey%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Chaos Monkey Plugin 0.4 and earlier does not perform permission checks in an HTTP endpoint, allowing attackers with Overall/Read permission to access the Chaos Monkey page and to see the history of actions.

item.title: CVE-2020-2322|2024-08-04T07:09:54.492Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20chaos%20monkey%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Chaos Monkey Plugin 0.3 and earlier does not perform permission checks in several HTTP endpoints, allowing attackers with Overall/Read permission to generate load and to generate memory leaks.
